headline: Fastenal Leans On Digital Growth While Managing Industrial Margin Pressures
summary: Fastenal (NasdaqGS:FAST) reported quarterly results highlighting a larger share of Q4 transactions coming through its FMI technology and other digital channels. Nearly half of Q4 sales were conducted via digital means, signaling a meaningful shift in how the company interacts with customers and fulfills orders. Management also discussed margin pressures and slower volume growth tied to ongoing challenges in the industrial economy. Fastenal, a major distributor of industrial and construction...
